Windows



Instalar python
	
	http://www.python.org/download/
	
Add your python 
	C:\Python27 to the path

Instalar psycopg2

	http://www.stickpeople.com/projects/python/win-psycopg/

Instalar easy_install

	http://pypi.python.org/pypi/setuptools

Instalar pip

	http://pypi.python.org/pypi/pip#downloads

Uncompress

>python setup.py install

Add your python c:\Python27\Scripts to the path

Instalar twython

	>pip install twython


Ubuntu



sudo apt-get install python-setuptools python-pip python-dev build-essential libpq-dev

sudo pip install --upgrade pip 

sudo pip install --upgrade virtualenv 

sudo apt-get install postgresql pgadmin3

pip install simplejson

pip install oauth2

pip install twython